* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 15-Apr-25 10:45 Page   1
*                                      EXERC5.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC5.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC5.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION  DIVISION.
     2 PROGRAM-ID.     EXERC5.
     3 AUTHOR.         YHAGO PESSOA.
     4 INSTALLATION.   FATEC-SP.
     5 DATE-WRITTEN.   18/03/2025.
     6 DATE-COMPILED. 15-Apr-25 10:45.
     7 SECURITY. APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICA-LO.
     8*REMARKS.  LE O REGISTRO DO ARQUIVO DE ENTRADA
     9*          CADALU(CODIGO,NOME,NOTA1,NOTA2 E FALTAS) E GRAVA
    10*          NO ARQUVIO DE SAIDA CADAPR(CODIGO,NOME,MEDIA)SOMENTE
    11*          AQUELES QUE APRESENTA NOTAS MAIORES QUE 6 E TIVEREM
    12*          MENOS QUE 19 FALTAS.
    13
    14 ENVIRONMENT     DIVISION.
    15 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
    16 SOURCE-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    17 OBJECT-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    18 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    19
    20 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    21 FILE-CONTROL.
    22     SELECT   CADALU      ASSIGN      TO       DISK
    23     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    24     SELECT   CADAPR        ASSIGN     TO       DISK
    25     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    26
    27 DATA           DIVISION.
    28 FILE SECTION.
    29
    30 FD  CADALU
    31     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    32     VALUE    OF FILE-ID    IS          "CADALU.DAT".
    33 01  REG-ENT.
    34     02 NUM-ENT           PIC 9(05).
    35     02 NOME-ENT          PIC X(20).
    36     02 NOTA1-ENT         PIC 9(02)V99.
    37     02 NOTA2-ENT         PIC 9(02)V99.
    38     02 FALTAS            PIC 9(02).
    39
    40 FD  CADAPR
    41     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    42     VALUE   OF FILE-ID    IS   "CADAPR.DAT".
    43 01  REG-SAI.
    44     02 NUM-SAI           PIC 9(05).
    45     02 NOME-SAI          PIC X(20).
    46     02 MEDIA-SAI         PIC 9(02)V99.
    47
    48 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    49     77 FIM-ARQ          PIC X(03)    VALUE "NAO".
    50     77 MEDIA-CONT       PIC 9(02)V99.
    51
    52 PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
    53
    54 EXEMPLO.
    55     PERFORM INICIO.
    56     PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    57       UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 15-Apr-25 10:45 Page   2
*                                      EXERC5.CBL
    58     PERFORM TERMINO
    59     STOP RUN.
    60 INICIO.
    61     OPEN INPUT CADALU
    62          OUTPUT CADAPR.
    63     PERFORM LEITURA.
    64
    65     LEITURA.
    66         READ CADALU
    67            AT END
    68            MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.
    69 PRINCIPAL.
    70     PERFORM GRAVACAO.
    71     PERFORM LEITURA.
    72
    73     GRAVACAO.
    74         COMPUTE MEDIA-CONT=(NOTA1-ENT + NOTA2-ENT)/2.
    75         IF MEDIA-CONT >= 7 AND FALTAS <= 18
    76             MOVE NUM-ENT TO NUM-SAI
    77             MOVE NOME-ENT TO NOME-SAI
    78             MOVE MEDIA-CONT TO MEDIA-SAI
    79             WRITE REG-SAI
    80        END-IF.
    81
    82 TERMINO.
    83     CLOSE CADALU
    84           CADAPR.
